Competitive Advantages
  A successful project implementation can result in a range of competitive advantages that promote success for the organisation and       make it worth pursuing. Broadly speaking, 
  
  Increasd performance 
  Reduced costs
  Better operational capability
  More staff satisfaction 
  
  Greater customer retention
  More brand loyalty 
  
  Less time-consuming processes
  Less wait times 
  More revenue
  Stronger  reputation 
  Efficient allocation of resources
  Distinguish organisation from competition 
